mil.emp3.mapengine.api

Class Capabilities

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.emp3.mapengine.api.Capabilities
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapEngineCapabilities

    public class Capabilities
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMapEngineCapabilities
    EMP3 Core queries this class to determine the capabilities supported by a specific map engine. Currently this includes: shapes and symbols that can be plotted, version of supported WMS.
